TITLE: Several People Hurt, Thousands Flee As Wildfire Rages In Northern California
SUMMARY: Evacuees described chunks of ashes raining down and heavy smoke that made it look like "the world was coming to an end."

TITLE: Plane Circling Mississippi City Threatens To Crash, Police Say
SUMMARY: Police say the pilot of a small airplane was circling over Tupelo, Mississippi, and threatening to crash the aircraft into a Walmart store.

TITLE: Memphis Teacher Abducted While Jogging
SUMMARY: Tennessee authorities are searching for Eliza Fletcher, who was forced into a vehicle while running near the University of Memphis campus.

TITLE: It Took Going To Prison To Recognize My Toxic Masculinity. Here’s How I Finally Changed.
SUMMARY: "I have witnessed prisoners and guards get beaten until their eyes could not open, for nothing more than calling someone a 'punk.'"

TITLE: 9 Migrants Are Found Dead In Rio Grande: Border Patrol
SUMMARY: Tragic toll followed hazardous crossing by desperate dozens, said officials.

TITLE: It’s Alive: New Yorker Gets A Surprise Package With Living Creatures Inside
SUMMARY: The lizards and iguanas were taken in by a nonprofit, which said that live animals are "often" delivered to the wrong address.

TITLE: Colorado State Fair Competition Names An Unlikely Winner: AI-Made Artwork
SUMMARY: The piece saw a storm of criticism this week as onlookers debated the use of artificial intelligence in the arts.
